==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|*overheren}}, from {{inh|en|ang|oferhīeran||to overhear, hear, disobey, disregard, neglect}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|over|hear}}. Cognate with {{cog|nl|overhoren||to hear, hear about}}, {{cog|de|überhören||to not hear, ignore}}, {{cog|da|overhøre||to overhear}}, {{cog|is|yfirheyra||to hear}}, {{cog|got|*𐌿𐍆𐌰𐍂𐌷𐌰𐌿𐍃𐌾𐌰𐌽|t=to disregard, disobey}} (in {{m|got|𐌿𐍆𐌰𐍂𐌷𐌰𐌿𐍃𐌴𐌹𐌽𐍃}}).

